{"id": 754, "genre": 1000, "title": "快来看一下这些手癌症状，你中枪了吗？", "description": "请跟我左手右手一个错动作，右手左手错动作重播。", "record_count": 3825, "comment_count": 27, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183718lCGJLY8gh175x6Wr.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-01-13T01:08:01Z", "questions": [{"id": 647, "title": "快来看一下这些手癌症状，你中枪了吗？", "content": "下面这些手癌症状你中枪了吗？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 40714, "content": "把“老板”打成“老爸”", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183016YRTHViolfrbUwPEp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40713, "content": "“壕”“号”“hao”了半天就是打不出一个“好”字", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183015wfs5Pptdv0ujZN14.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40715, "content": "装不在：“你好，我现在不在请稍后练习（联系） ”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193608b4Lkz5uqi3U7ScX0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40716, "content": "别人问我“你有喜欢的人吗”把“有”回成了“you”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193609yMAcfs78owTgl2nu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40717, "content": "发红包（又TM）不小心多加了个0", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193609HRtbfqDlOh3FQM8K.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40723, "content": "打蛋时，蛋壳总会随着鸡蛋滑进碗里", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182951AXbsuM3q5968JOaE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40718, "content": "泡了五分钟的方便面，撕调料包酱料都洒到手上", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182857iYgVxHMLNlfbPeoD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40719, "content": "糊上泡沫刮胡子时，十有八九会刮伤自己", "image": "img/option/option/201606071936101iSmVnZ8O4YRATWl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40725, "content": "刮胡子没什么，试试屏息静气画眼线结果戳进眼睛", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193611fy1LspSBHdCQzab6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40724, "content": "别问我洗脸为什么会弄湿自己的衣领和袖口", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182951JrmNSg7BCRvGlduH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40720, "content": "永远搓不开超市的塑料袋", "image": "img/option/option/201607021830160PfdBjMJQXHT39iL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 40722, "content": "通宵熬夜写完稿子退出保存时点了“否”", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193611w9ORWFhSsbezTV3c.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}